Perhaps, dreaming is the time when our left brain shuts down (which 
is attached to the physical - outward realm) and the right brain, 
which has been suppressed by the left, is now allowed to interact 
with the spirit realm (which is its purpose).  

Bruce, don&#39;t you know there are two people in everyone...it&#39;s just a 
choice whether we want to be in our &quot;right&quot; mind (or not)!  ;)

